'''Aquilie water''' was very pure, bottled spring water, favored by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] during the height of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]]. [[Tol Sivron]] and [[Bevel Lemelisk]] drank some while presenting the [[Death Star plans/Legends|Death Star plans]] to [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]; [[Wilhuff Tarkin/Legends|Wilhuff Tarkin]], however, turned it down in favor of [[coffee]].

